Project Haining Wanpu was located in Haining. Both land parcels were in commercial use and acquired directly from local government. Phase I land was acquited in 2015 at a consideration of CNY1.2M with LUR expired in 2065. Phase II land was acquired in 2017 at a consideration of CNY1.5M with LUR expired in 2067.

The land lots of Project Haining Wanpu were amortised using straight-line method with 50 years of useful life and zero residual value. Cash and cash equivalents were depreciated using straight-line method with 20 years of useful life and 4% residual value. As at this report date, Project Haining Wanpu was completed but no final accounts had been conducted. Though management said that most of the primary contracts had been verified and accounted, the original costs may still not be finalised. Potential under-estimated construction payables and CAPEX commitments may still exist. Management said there was no CAPEX plan at current stage.

SUMMARY: Used entity 'Haining Wanpu' with amounts: CNY197.5K (cash and cash equivalents), CNY1.2M (Phase I land), CNY1.5M (Phase II land)
